description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions


Kate and Leisha discuss cowlicks, shaving their heads, and dressing for their age. They then answer some of your questions about: what's your calling, loving yourself, working in Hollywood, getting back with your ex, and funerals.


Get Tickets To Their Live Show:

https://www.events.loopedlive.com/pants
